00:49:06.280 --> 00:49:08.300
<i>Han ville bare have bolden.</i>

703
00:49:09.360 --> 00:49:11.420
<i>Han ville lave alle mulige afleveringer.</i>

704
00:49:12.480 --> 00:49:14.230
<i>Gascoigne står klar,</i>

705
00:49:14.280 --> 00:49:17.940
<i>lobber den derind, og Platt har scoret.</i>

706
00:49:19.080 --> 00:49:21.470
<i>Han elsker den store scene.
